### Read a user by id
GET http://localhost:4000/user-api/user

### create new user
POST http://localhost:4000/user-api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username":"Harish",
    "password":"Harish",
    "email":"Harish@gmail.com",
    "age":19
}

### user login
POST http://localhost:4000/user-api/auth
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email":"Harish@gmail.com",
    "password":"Harish"
}

### Update a user
PUT http://localhost:4000/user-api/users/69aa98336ad966bfbc13b0fc
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username":"Harish",
    "password":"Harish@159",
    "email":"harish08@gmail.com",
    "age":19
}

### Delete a user by id
DELETE http://localhost:4000/user-api/users/69aa98336ad966bfbc13b0fc


